                    <div class="span12">
                        <h1>Army vice chief walks through brigade command program to witness Army’s newest assessment tool</h1>
                        <p class="small">By Eric Pilgrim<span>August 13, 2020</span></p>
                        <section class="alt-social-bar">
  <ul>
        <li class="social-button-sm twitter-button">
            <a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.army.mil%2Farticle%2F238143%2Farmy_vice_chief_walks_through_brigade_command_program_to_witness_armys_newest_assessment_tool&amp;text=Army%20vice%20chief%20walks%20through%20brigade%20command%20program%20to%20witness%20Army%E2%80%99s%20newest%20assessment%20tool"><span>Share on Twitter</span></a>
