                <img alt="Army vice chief walks through brigade command program to witness Army’s newest assessment tool" src="https://api.army.mil/e2/c/images/2020/08/13/6502b3ee/size0-full.jpg" />
              </a>
                              <span class="ss-move ss-prev">
                  <span class="ss-move-button"></span>
