                <span class="caption-author"> (Photo Credit: Eric Pilgrim, Fort Knox News)</span>
              </span>
              <a href="https://api.army.mil/e2/c/images/2020/08/13/6502b3ee/original.jpg" title="View original" target="_blank">VIEW ORIGINAL</a>
            </span>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
                      <figure class="photo">
